<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.9.9">
<l>kamalak kaṇṇaṉeṉ kaṇṇiṉuḷḷāṉ kāṇpa ṉavaṉkaṇka ḷālē</l>
<l>yamalaṅka ḷāka viḻikku maimpula ṉumavaṉ mūrtti</l>
<l>kamalat tayaṉnampi taṉṉaik kaṇṇuta lāṉoṭun tōṟṟi</l>
<l>yamalat teyvattō ṭulaka mākkiyeṉ neṟṟiyu ḷāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one with lotus eyes is in my eyes. I see him with [my] eyes.</l>
<l>All [my] five sense look attentively at his form, so as to become spotless.</l>
<l>Making appear the lord Ayaṉ from the lotus along with the one with the forehead eye,</l>
<l>creating the world along with the spotless gods he is on my brow.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
